the theory of everything : the origin and fate of the univers it has come to our attention that the book `` the theory of everything : the origin and fate of the universe '' has been published . professor hawking would like to make it clear that he has not endorsed this book . the text was written by him many years ago , however the material has already been published in books such as 'a brief history of time ' . a complaint was made to the federal trade commission in the us in the hope that they would prevent the publication . we would urge you not to purchase this book in the belief that professor hawking was involved in its creation .